text: David Pasqualucci is an Italian archer. He was born on 27 June 1996. Pasqualucci competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics.David PasqualucciDavid PASQUALUCCI ==Biography== David Pasqualucci entered his first international competitions in 2013. He achieved his first global podium in 2014 when he won the bronze in the men's individual classic archery event at the junior indoor championship. == References == Category:Italian archers Category:Olympians for Italy Category:Sportspeople from Lazio Category:Living people Category:1996 births
